attributes.name: groups
attributes.description: List of groups that user belongs to

attributes.name: preferred_username
attributes.description: The primary username that represents the user

scopes.name: dcr_register
scopes.description: Allows to register client using dynamic client registration endpoint when it's configured to require initial access token

scopes.name: introspect_tokens
scopes.description: Allows to introspect tokens

scopes.name: list_clients_with_access
scopes.description: Allows to list clients that user granted access

scopes.name: revoke_client_access
scopes.description: Allows to revoke client access granted by user and remove all tokens

scopes.name: revoke_tokens
scopes.description: Allows to revoke tokens

scopes.name: address
scopes.description: This scope value requests access to the address claim.

scopes.name: email
scopes.description: This scope value requests access to the email and email_verified claims.

scopes.name: offline_access
scopes.description: This scope value requests offline access using refresh token.

scopes.name: openid
scopes.description: This scope value requests access to the sub claim which uniquely identifies the user.

scopes.name: phone
scopes.description: This scope value requests access to the phone_number and phone_number_verified claims.

scopes.name: profile
scopes.description: This scope value requests access to the end-user's default profile claims, which are: name, family_name, given_name, middle_name, nickname, preferred_username, profile, picture, website, gender, birthdate, zoneinfo, locale, and updated_at.

scopes.name: transient_otp
scopes.description: Allows to send one-time passwords via email or SMS

scopes.name: manage_consents
scopes.description: Allows to grant and revoke user consents

scopes.name: view_consents
scopes.description: Allows to view user consents
